 publication is the prose book, Self into Song, based on three poetry lectures delivered in the Bloodaxe-Newcastle University Lecture Series. She is currently professor in creative writing at Bangor University, and is a fellow of the Royal Society of Literature. Her latest collection is <a href=\"http://www.serenbooks.com/book/de-chiricos-threads/9781854115348\">De Chirico's Threads, published by Seren Books</a>.</p>","bylineImageUrl":"https://static.guim.co.uk/artsblog/authorpics/carol_rumens.jpg","firstName":"carol","lastName":"rumens","r2ContributorId":"25452"}],"elements":[{"id":"6f02eaaf79f2fe228e8e87b1e872e80baa549aa0","relation":"main","type":"image","assets":[{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"https://media.guim.co.uk/6f02eaaf79f2fe228e8e87b1e872e80baa549aa0/0_1_2626_1575/2000.jpg","typeData":{"altText":"the night sky.","caption":"‘Glow-in-the-dark’ … the night sky.","credit":"Photograph: Martin Hunter/AP","photographer":"Martin Hunter","source":"AP","width":"2000","height":"1200","secureFile":"https://media.guim.co.uk/6f02eaaf79f2fe228e8e87b1e872e80baa549aa0/0_1_2626_1575/2000.jpg","displayCredit":"true","mediaId":"6f02eaaf79f2fe228e8e87b1e872e80baa549aa0","imageType":"Photograph","suppliersReference":"FRA505","mediaApiUri":"https://api.media.gutools.co.uk/images/6f02eaaf79f2fe228e8e87b1e872e80baa549aa0","copyright":"AP2007"}},{"type":"image","mimeType":"image/jpeg","file":"https://media.guim.co.uk/6f02eaaf79f2fe228e8e87b1e872e80baa549aa0/0_1_2626_1575/1000.jpg","typeData":{"altText":"the night sky.","caption":"‘Glow-in-the-dark’ … the night sky.","credit":"Photograph: Martin Hunter/AP","photographer":"Martin Hunter","source":"AP","width":"1000","height":"600","secureFile":"https://media.guim.co.uk/6f02eaaf79f2fe228e8e87b1e872e80baa549aa0/0_1_2626_1575/1000.jpg","displayCredit":"true","mediaId":"6f02eaaf79f2fe228e8e87b1e872e80baa549aa0","imageType":"Photograph","suppliersReference":"FRA505","mediaApiUri":"https://api.media.gutools.co.uk/images/